{"tid":1602454,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"沙地亞拉伯開放旅遊簽證比觀光客","createTime":"2019-09-29T11:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T03:50:49.000Z","uid":141263,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1173b488f2ac5f25a170a19e66d9604ed5126168","tid":1602454,"uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"都算大新聞，冇人講？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沙特阿拉伯首次開放旅遊簽證給外國人，大約50個國家及地區，包括中國、美國、澳洲及日本等受惠。<br />\n<br />\n沙特表示，旅客即日起可以透過網上申請旅遊簽證，但非穆斯林仍然禁止進入聖城麥加，外國遊客亦繼續不可以飲酒，不過女性只需穿著得體，毋須穿著黑色長罩袍。<br />\n<br />\n沙特阿拉伯是保守的穆斯林國家，原本只向外勞、商人及朝聖者開放簽證，今次開放旅遊簽證，是王儲穆罕默德主張推動經濟多元發展的一部分<br />\n<br />\n整左條片介紹，大家多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KAb-qjFj6Rc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKAb-qjFj6Rc&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=bf12c580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KAb-qjFj6Rc</a>"},{"pid":"9bb1130de74fa2613a41a6d4d5464ef1ec1e260a","tid":1602454,"uid":35746,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"但非穆斯林仍然禁止進入聖城麥加，外國遊客亦繼續不可以飲酒<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"b9c8f9c034c8492b85b0fd3320fed1fd4068d129","tid":1602454,"uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bb1130de74fa2613a41a6d4d5464ef1ec1e260a","tid":1602454,"uid":35746,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"但非穆斯林仍然禁止進入聖城麥加，外國遊客亦繼續不可以飲酒<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:21:01.000Z","msg":"觀光都好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n體驗下姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw唔可以食豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08181c5bc5bc5411